For those who are interested on trying out journalling filesystem.  I have
made a kernel rpm which supports XFS, JFS, Ext3 and ReiserFS.  You can get it
at 
ftp://ftp.cwlinux.com/pub/downloads/journaling_fs/kernel.
  Comments are
welcome.
-Andrew
